-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://syntax.fm/944\" target=\"_blank\">https://syntax.fm/944</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100060415\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=28ec7194&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dYr1zr0Paoj8xCpyiathNRdibaVjwIpxfZhkonaicpVYVD81KQv0icDNDoAuOPxykPqAWOvzyFQYA0vQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;color: black;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Developer Tea：通过刻意练习提升工程领导技能</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 本期节目深入探讨了刻意练习的概念，它让最优秀的人在从体育到写作到工程等各个领域中脱颖而出。解释了为什么它不仅仅是重复或经验，以及为什么将其应用到你的职业生涯中可以带来快速改进。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 12px;padding: 16px 20px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.476px;text-align: left;display: flex;align-items: center;background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246)